Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.44,0:01:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好  出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there's that and here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊  是脏鱼锅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wey, wook, it's Windward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.52,0:01:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏鱼锅要丧班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Windward's wolling to work
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在哪丧班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where does he work?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.27,0:01:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在穴堡黄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wat the Wusty Wab?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.93,0:01:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是在说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某种没营养的暗号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some kind of stupid secret code?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是俱乐部的会员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause you're not a member of the club
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.65,0:01:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了当白痴以外  加入还有什么条件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does it take to be a member besides being a moron?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moron
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as a requirement
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算你试过了  也不能加入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you couldn't get in even if you tried
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要让你们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll have you know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.58,0:02:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是加入了全海底20家高级俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I am a member of over 20 different
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,exclusive clubs all across the sea bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.90,0:02:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说的是他鼻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something about his nose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.82,0:02:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你跟你鼻子绝对塞不进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you and your nose will definitely not fit in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个废物怎么知道塞不塞得进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you two zeros know about fitting in?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反倒是你们该求我加进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you should be begging me to join
Dialogue: 3,0:02:27.65,0:02:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  不行
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.65,0:02:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.34,0:02:29.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:29.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.96,0:02:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.37,0:02:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.80,0:02:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能加入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't join
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.35,0:02:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能加入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't join
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't get in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么破玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面根本没地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no room up here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直就想提醒你这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what we've been trying to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经困在这上面三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been stuck up here for three days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就提醒过你塞不进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We told you you wouldn't fit in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.67,0:02:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那既然你进来了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, since you're here, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就给你举行个新会员加入仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll give you the new member initiation
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入俱乐部  欢迎加入俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our club, welcome to our club
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎章鱼哥  欢迎章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome Squidward, welcome, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎章鱼哥  欢迎章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Squidward, welcome, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都给我闭上你们的臭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut your half-wit pie holes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在不想  以后也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do not now nor will I ever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.71,0:03:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成为你们这破烂俱乐部的会员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,want to be a member of your stupid club
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许个愿吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make a wish, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能出那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This didn't just happen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托告诉我没出那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me that didn't happen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're lost
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no way out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,困在荒郊野岭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stuck in the middle of nowhere
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还跟海绵宝宝跟派大星一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with Spongebob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.27,0:03:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么我一生每11分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why must every 11 minutes of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.22,0:04:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都会充满不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be filled with misery?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,振作点  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会更糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It could be worse
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  你可能会秃头还长个大鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could be bald and have a big nose
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the end
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没有  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,292)}逝者安息\N海绵宝宝    派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要团结一致  我们一定会没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to be fine as long as we stick together
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  我们是个俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, we're a club
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我们有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides, we have this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是魔法海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The magic conch shell
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快问话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask it something
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快问话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask it something
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.57,0:04:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺  我会结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic conch shell, will I ever get married?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许将来会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe someday
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就一破玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is just a stupid toy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can that possibly help us?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.98,0:04:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以质疑魔法海螺的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we must never question the wisdom of the magic conch
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俱乐部成员都会听从它的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The club always takes its advice
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后才做事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before we do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺无所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The shell knows all
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, magic conch shell
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办才能走出这片海草林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what do we need to do to get out of the kelp forest?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.90,0:05:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺发话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The shell has spoken
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能光坐着什么都不做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't just sit here and do nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们居然要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you two are going
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听从玩具的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to take advice from a toy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会找到重回理智的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am going to find my way back to sanity
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两位伤心小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But don't you two sad clowns
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.32,0:05:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别等你们马戏团塌了就来找我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come crying to me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when your circus tent comes crashing down
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伤心小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sad clown
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sad
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,clown
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.00,0:05:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都来过这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was already here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which way do I go?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm lost
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全找不到路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hopelessly lost
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也没法走出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招吧  海绵宝宝跟派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that, Spongebob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全离不开这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no way out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.57,0:06:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们神奇智慧海螺俱乐部情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it going over there at Club Shell for Brains?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.07,0:06:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道章鱼哥俱乐部今晚吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's on the menu for Club Squidward tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很香吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that smell good, Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都好几天没吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten in days
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about you, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星是铁  饭是钢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A big boy's got to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准你们吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't have any
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道什么原因吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And do you know why, Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.10,0:07:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原因就是你们俱乐部主席是个海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because your club president is a shell
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们听了我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you had listened to me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会有食物  避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd have food, shelter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有熊熊的篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a roaring fire
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.00,0:07:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而你们非要听个会说话的蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but instead you listened to a talking clam
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫你们什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that tells you nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得好像你们一切问题的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause the answers to all your problems
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会从天上掉下来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will fall right out of the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从天上掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fall right out of the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就快从天上掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, we're falling right out of the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须卸货减少负重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to drop the load
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,414)}卸货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:41.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1074,410)}野餐补给公司
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赞美魔法海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Praise the magic conch
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.37,0:08:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你们那边的吃的还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob, that sure is a lot of food you got there
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是魔法海螺的赠礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a gift from the magic conch
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西看着都好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything sure looks delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烟熏香肠  我最爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smoked sausages, my favorite
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道我先前都是在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you know I was just kidding around earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我还是俱乐部的一员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm still part of the club, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.74,0:08:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟俱乐部要团结一致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And after all, the club got to stick together
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.89,0:08:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一朝当会员  终生成会员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once a member, always a member
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敬俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the club
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.95,0:09:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要先吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What shall I eat first
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.80,0:09:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意大利面  火鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the spaghetti, the turkey
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汤  罐头肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the soup, the canned meat?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么不问问魔法海螺呢  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the magic conch, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得好像我真会问一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, like that'll happen
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不如先去问魔法脚趾甲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right after I consult the magic toenail
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你是在质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, are you questioning
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺的权威吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the authority of the magic conch?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海螺向我们恩赐了这场盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The conch is the one who gave us this banquet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个有版权保护的海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This copyrighted conch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我们俱乐部的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the cornerstone of our organization
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能他不当咱同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not a brother
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys have it all wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.85,0:09:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱这块塑料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love this piece of plastic
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, there
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺  我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic conch, I was wondering
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该吃意大利面还是火鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should I have the spaghetti or the turkey?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neither
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那能不能喝汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then how about the soup?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能吃东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have anything to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.26,0:09:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能几个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean no?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starving here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺  章鱼哥可不可以吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic conch, could Squidward have some of this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味好吃超可口的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yummy, delicious, super-terrific sandwich?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.85,0:10:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不可以吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味好吃超可口的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yummy, delicious, super terrific sandwich?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能吃点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have something to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能吃点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have something to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.12,0:10:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能吃点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have something to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.03,0:10:28.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:28.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了不能你就不能说别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you say anything else but no?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请再问一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try asking again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能吃点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have something to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, are you all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许应该问海螺他有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should ask the shell if he's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, anyone there?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们需要救援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you folks need some help?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm saved
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都不知道我见到你有多高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know how happy I am to see you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经困在这好几周了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been stranded out here for weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身边还有两个呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with these two barnacle-heads
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他们的魔法海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and their magic conch shell
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic conch shell?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic conch
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们俱乐部的会员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A club member
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海螺要我来救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My conch told me to come save you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为魔法海螺欢呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray for the magic conches
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了魔法海螺  我们应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, magic conch, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hail the magic conch
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法海螺万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hail the magic conch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.81,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(401,429)}我的漂亮海马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:12:01.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347.802,488)\frz24.93}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz24.93\pos(299.802,428)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz24.93\pos(457.802,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz24.93\pos(311.802,414)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz24.93\pos(517.802,682)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,springtime in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有海洋生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All sea creatures
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对换季天生敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have an innate sense of the seasonal changes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,例如海星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like the starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对四处的环境飞快地感知后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A quick survey of his environment
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he knows that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's spring
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是海星脱下了冬装
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The starfish then sheds his winter coat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妥善保存  以备将来过冬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and stores it away safe for winter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好打电话找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better call the doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我得了春天热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I've got spring fever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  小花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, little flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a lovely day?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟小花问好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say hello to the flowers yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  小花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道章鱼哥对花粉过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I didn't know Squidward had hay fever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do him a kindness
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,种点不容易过敏的花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and planet some hypoallergenic flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,茁壮成长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on your way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you're thirsty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要一直盯着你不放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking my eyes off you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,三天后
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does this keep happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的海马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a magnificent sea horse
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要驯服它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall tame her
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天晓得能达成什么样的成就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knows what we can accomplish
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.57,0:14:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由于它行为神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Because of her mysterious behavior
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我决定将其取名为神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have decided to name her Mystery"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但既然我想到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它还很优雅威严
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she's also very graceful and majestic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.86,0:14:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许应该要取名优雅或者威严
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should name her Grace or Majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.87,0:14:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者黛比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or Debbie
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它一定看到我的花朵书签了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She must have spotted my floral bookmark
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's coming this way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a girl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是个会说话的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just a talking sponge is all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,190)}帽子
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我一生中最棒的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that was the greatest day of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会永远当上好朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll be friends forever?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就当你觉得会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a "yes"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  还在骑着机器去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, still riding to work on the machine I see
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么话都别说  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了你的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember your karma
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(902,404)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoa, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班期间你就在这边等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you wait out here until I'm done with work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下班时候见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at the end of my shift
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  蟹老板装了个摇摇车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, Mr. Krabs put in a kiddy ride
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不来玩玩看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找不到投币口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't find the coin slot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇摇车发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kiddie ride on the loose
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面是在闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A monster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓跑了我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scaring away me customers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是怪物  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a monster, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a horse
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名叫神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Her name is Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才神秘  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a mystery, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get rid of it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托蟹老板  让它留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Krabs, let her stay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不会伤着大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She won't hurt nobody no how
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟神秘只能留一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's either you or Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就取名黛比好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I should have named her Debbie
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最终还是除掉了那匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for finally getting rid of that horse
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在能除掉章鱼哥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now if we could just get rid of Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先把你安置在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just keep you back here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等派大星做完我要的马厩就能出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until Patrick finishes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that stable I asked him to build
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再八小时就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only eight more hours
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,十二秒后
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't come out yet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是蟹老板看到你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If old man Krabs sees you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会失业的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll lose my job
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you're hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要吃午饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some lunch?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘘  不能吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shh, girl, you got to be quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, what was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那匹马在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that horse in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在模仿神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just doing my imitation of Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续努力干活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, keep working on it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太险了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起不能再闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And from now on no more high jinks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我的餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, where's my order?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,托盘底下看了没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you look under the tray?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.09,0:18:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.94,0:18:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能不能好好上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, could you just get my order?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They vanished
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.70,0:18:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你觉得蟹堡王是不是闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, do you think the Krusty Krab is haunted?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是鬼等下来找我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if they come for me next?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须先逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上没有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's no ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怕你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In case you've forgotten
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就告诉你工作流程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here's how things work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I order the food
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你制作餐点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cook the food
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顾客取餐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then the customer gets the food
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连续干个40年然后死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We do that for 40 years and then we die
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉很划算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a pretty good deal to me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hear you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.15,0:19:11.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:11.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跟蟹老板说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都控制好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it all under control
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说你刚刚有说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now then, you were saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧把餐做好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get my order
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.87,0:19:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘  你吃了我帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mystery, you ate my hat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘  你吃了我锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mystery, you ate my spatula
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,830)}肉饼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把蟹黄堡肉饼都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ate all the Krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃了炉子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ate the stove
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃了老头简金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ate old man Jankins
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想成为累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a burden
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.24,0:19:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们厨房出了一点小状况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Folks, we have a minor situation going on in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's our food?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我午餐时间就这一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my only lunch hour
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's old man Jankins?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正这边的东西也不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The food's no good here anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what's going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就去问问牛仔宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ask Cowbob RanchPants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他忠实的伙伴巨能吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his faithful companion Sir Eats-a-lot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  那堆外号什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, what's the meaning of all these nicknames?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的戴维琼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,David H. Jones
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘吃蟹黄堡肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mystery got a bellyache from eating Krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就泡了小苏打给它喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I made her a bicarbonate of soda
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错过了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I miss?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我果然没看错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, my eyes are correct
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.47,0:20:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫你除掉那匹马  结果你却没除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still have that horse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after I ordered you to get rid of it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在只能让我亲自彻底除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now, I'm going to get rid of it once and for all
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.75,0:20:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别让我抛弃神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please don't make me give up Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你认为它只是匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you think she's just a horse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我跟你说  它不仅仅是匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but she's more than that, I tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它会听我话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She listens to me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.77,0:20:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能理解我说的话  我也理解它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She understands everything I say and I understand her
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁把这碗洋葱放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who left this bowl of onions here?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.27,0:20:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你的故事感动了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, your story has touched me heart
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信不信由你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道抛弃好朋友是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what's it like to give up a best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我五岁那时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was five years old
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的父亲给了我一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and me father gave me a dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很爱那块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loved that dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像爱护兄弟一样爱着它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loved it like a brother
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.84,0:21:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我和那块钱形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and that dollar went everywhere together
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那块钱怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the dollar, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一天  在海滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one day at the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.97,0:21:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气很热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it was so hot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又很渴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I was so thirsty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.28,0:21:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把它花了买汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spent it on a soda
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.62,0:21:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you get out of here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点在于
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The point is, son
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.02,0:21:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然很难受  但有时也得学会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sometimes you have to set things free
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even though it's hard
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.15,0:21:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at her
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.10,0:21:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它想念大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She misses the great outdoors
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开阔的原野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wide open spaces
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.15,0:21:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连绵的绿草
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the rolling green pastures
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.94,0:21:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厨房并不能成为马儿的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The kitchen is no place for a live horse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.76,0:21:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, girl, you're free to go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不能留住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't keep you anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.22,0:22:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你很难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard for you to understand
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.05,0:22:21.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但蟹老板说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:21.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Mr. Krabs is right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.80,0:22:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你属于大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You belong in the wild
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还在等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来我再也不要你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I don't want you anymore?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走吧  你这傻动物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get out of here, you stupid, dumb animal
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, she's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也看不到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll never see her again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, son
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做出了正确的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did the proper thing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.43,0:22:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它现在自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's free now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们无权
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we have no right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.07,0:22:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把野生动物剥离自然栖息地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to separate that wild animal from its natural habitat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.57,0:23:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子神秘吃了份餐后沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like ol' Mystery had an after-dinner salad
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住那匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get that horse
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.87,0:23:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.87,0:23:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.07,0:23:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.84,0:23:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.52,0:23:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mystery, come back here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:12.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,208)}帽子
